# E2E Fixtures Location

- Store all E2E fixtures only in the root `fixtures/` folder.
- Do not add fixture files under `tests/**` (for example `tests/fixtures` or `tests/logistics/fixtures`).
- When moving or adding fixtures, update all imports/paths to use `fixtures/...`.
- Keep fixture naming consistent:
  - runtime/local fixture data: `fixtures/*.json`
  - fixture helpers/modules: `fixtures/*.ts`
  - Playwright fixture wrappers: `fixtures/*.fixture.ts`

## Examples

- ✅ `fixtures/reportFixtures.ts`
- ✅ `fixtures/fixtures.local.json`
- ✅ `fixtures/logisticsApp.fixture.ts`
- ❌ `tests/logistics/fixtures/reportFixtures.ts`
- ❌ `tests/fixtures/fixtures.local.json`
